024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Andre-3000-rapper-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Andre-3000-rapper-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">André 3000</a>宣布了他最近的实验长笛专辑《New Blue Sun》的新一波巡演日期。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/outkast">Outkast</a>说唱歌手去年 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-announces-first-solo-album-in-17-years-full-of-flute-music-preorder-3538764">出人意料地放弃了一个长达 87 分钟的项目</a>，这是他 17 年来的首张个人专辑。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-announces-first-new-blue-sun-tour-dates-3576101">继今年早些时候的美国巡演之后</a>，André 3000 宣布将于今年秋天在美国进行一系列新的巡演。从九月开始，安德烈将在新奥尔良的欧菲姆剧院拉开帷幕，访问休斯顿、西雅图、温哥华和盐湖城等一系列新城市。</p><p>然后，他将于 11 月 14 日在亚特兰大福克斯剧院举行新的巡演，结束他的新巡演。请参阅下面的所有日期 - 门票今天（6 月 26 日）上午 10 点（美国中部时间）上午 10 点（美国东部时间上午 11 点，英国夏令时下午 4 点）开始销售，因此<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fandre-3000-tickets%2Fartist%2F3102409" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请在此处购买：</a> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8pQZFruRDi/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4